    <stitle>CE 200, CE 300 - HOOD, GRILLE, FENDERS AND BUMPER - Install - Fog Lights</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Fog Lights</title>
        <para>Insert the fog light assembly into the center opening of the front bumper and locate the mounting hole.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Align and insert fog light assembly and mounting bracket on lower cross member bar. Install
                flat washer and lock nut, finger tighten. Adjust the fog light direction and tighten mounting lock nut.
            </para>
            <figure id="f09009104" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figg09/G09009104.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                         scalefitheight="272px"/>
                <caption>Figure 101. Fog Light Assembly</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. FOG LIGHT ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. DRIVER SIDE FRAME RAIL</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. FRONT END HARNESS CONNECTION</callout1>
                    <callout1>4. FRONT CROSS MEMBER ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Plug fog light harness into headlight assembly harness.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
